  "body": "When the `dependency update` command fetches the required chart from the repo it always takes the latest one, not considering the specified version at all.\n\nI took a look at the code and the problem seem to be here : https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/blob/master/cmd/helm/downloader/manager.go#L337\nThe loop returns even if the version was not found. I did a quick test locally and it behaves as expected when this line is removed.\n",
